# lintian      - static checks; run before sharing the .deb
# pbuilder     - clean-chroot builds; catches missing build-deps
# sbuild       - similar to pbuilder, used by debian buildds
# fpm          - multi-format packager (.deb/.rpm/.pkg); minimal config
# cargo-deb    - emit a .deb from a rust crate
# nfpm         - emit a .deb (or .rpm) from a single yaml config; common in go projects
